entries.femaleVariant: Mmm, your heart chakra looks a little out of whack, babe.
And your aura… it needs tending, baby. You've gotta brush it daily. It's just no good if you don't.
I can release it for you, but you'd have to watch out for negative energy fields... And avoid mean reds, anything red.
Ah, thanks, Misty. You're the best.
Hey, V.
Dr. Vektor will see you now.
I'll sit tight over here. Me 'n' Misty got a little catchin' up to do.
V, yo, listen up! I talked to Dex while you were in with the doc.
OK, do my best to talk us up.
Make sure your hands are clean and caress the filaments of light along their length.
They'll be strong, then. They'll be firm.
Uh-huh. Firm.
He's waitin' in his ride. For you. Ain't but a hop to where he's parked, next to Gramsci Burgers.
You look pleased.
'Cause I am, always! Makes for easier livin'. But…
We got a new job lined up. From a big hitter at the Afterlife.
Oh, is it gonna be dangerous?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="mi amor" b="Don't you worry, " a=". We're bullet-proof."/>
